--------
Type in and [Run] the next example. Don't forget, you
can press [F1 ] to run a program, instead of triggering the
[Run] option with your mouse. When the first line has
appeared, the program will wait for you to press a key
before printing the last line on screen.

 Print "Wait"
 Wait Key
 Print "Continue"

